About this property

Suvastu Resort

When visiting Swat, Suvastu Resort is a great choice to consider. Free perks include WiFi and self-parking.

Frequently asked questions

Does Suvastu Resort offer free cancellation for a full refund?
Yes, Suvastu Resort does have fully refundable room rates available to book on our site. If you’ve booked a fully refundable room rate, this can be cancelled up to a few days before check-in, depending on the property's cancellation policy. Just make sure that you check this property's cancellation policy for the exact terms and conditions.
Are pets allowed at Suvastu Resort?
Sorry, pets aren't allowed.
Is parking offered on site at Suvastu Resort?
Yes, there's free self parking.
What are the check-in and check-out times at Suvastu Resort?
Check-in start time: 2:00 PM; check-in end time: 5:30 PM. Check-out time is 12:30 PM.
Are there restaurants at or near Suvastu Resort?
Yes, there's an on-site restaurant.
